data.value: Wake up!! CAPTAIN !!! You are the commander of the ocean campaign. > You will have been challenged by enemies in 9x9 battlefield. > Please get to place your battleships on your play area. > When placement finished, Trying to fire enemy by taking the shoot into their play area. > Automatic system will notify you of the hit target or missed target. > If you have a hit target on enemy ship, you will get one more fire. > Let destroy enemy ship and win the battle!!!
